#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Enter the name of the <guilabel>Network</guilabel> here. You may create "
#| "as many entries in the <guilabel>Server List</guilabel> screen with the "
#| "same <guilabel>Network</guilabel> as you like."
