#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I start &konversation;, I'd like to connect to a server without joining "
"any channels. How do I do that?"
msgstr ""
"Når jeg starter &konversation; vil jeg forbindes til en server uden at gå "
"med i nogen kanaler. Hvordan gør jeg det?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Edit Server</link> screen, "
"leave the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> frame empty."
msgstr ""
"Efterlad feltet <guilabel>Kanaler</guilabel> tomt på skærmen <link linkend="
"\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Redigér server</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3209
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&konversation; won't connect to any servers. What is wrong.?"
msgid "&konversation; won't connect to any servers. What is wrong?"
msgstr "&konversation; forbinder ikke til nogen server. Hvad er der  galt?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3212
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several things that could be wrong."
msgstr "Der er flere ting som kan være galt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that you have entered the correct <guilabel>Server name</guilabel> "
"and the correct <guilabel>Port</guilabel> in the <link linkend=\"serverlist-"
"addserver\">Add Server</link> screen."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for dig at du har indtastet det rigtige <guilabel>Servernavn</guilabel> "
"og den rigtige <guilabel>Port</guilabel> på skærmen <link linkend="
"\"serverlist-addserver\">Tilføj server</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the output in the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Server "
"Messages</link> screen for any error messages. Did the server reject the "
"connection because of a bad password? Did the server reject the connection "
"because it requires <acronym>IDENTD</acronym> and your computer did not "
"respond to the <acronym>IDENT</acronym> request? Did you check the SSL "
"protocol box but the server does not support SSL?"
msgstr ""
"Kontrollér udskriften på skærmen <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour"
"\">Servermeddelelser</link> for om der er nogen fejlmeddelelser. Afslog  "
"serveren forbindelsen på grund af et forkert kodeord? Afslog serveren "
"forbindelsen fordi den kræver <acronym>IDENTD</acronym> og din maskine ikke "
"svarede på forespørgsler om <acronym>IDENT</acronym>? Markerede du feltet "
"SSL-protokol, men serveren understøtter ikke SSL?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are behind a firewall, make sure the correct ports are enabled. "
"&konversation; needs the following ports enabled:"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du er bag en brandmur, så sørg for at de rigtige porte er aktiverede. "
"&konversation; kræver at følgende porte er aktiverede:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outgoing TCP 6667 (or the port of the server you connect to)"
msgstr "Udgående TCP 6667 (eller porten på serveren som du forbinder til)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incoming TCP 113 (if the server requires IDENTD)"
msgstr "Indkommende TCP 113 (hvis serveren kræver IDENTD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3239
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url="
#| "\"http://www.irchelp.org/irchelp/networks/connectprob.html\">irchelp.org</"
#| "ulink>."
msgid ""
"For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/irchelp/wio/blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"For mere information om &irc;-forbindelsesproblemer, se <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.irchelp.org/irchelp/networks/connectprob.html\">irchelp.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
